18
00:03:23,385 --> 00:03:24,385
(To think your heart)

19
00:03:25,023 --> 00:03:27,343
(is void of all selfish desires.)

20
00:03:46,997 --> 00:03:48,157
Human hearts are restless

21
00:03:48,647 --> 00:03:49,877
