44
00:05:41,300 --> 00:05:41,890
All right.

45
00:05:42,168 --> 00:05:43,847
All of Qingqiu's local specialties

46
00:05:43,848 --> 00:05:44,698
are here.

47
00:05:44,968 --> 00:05:45,578
Yanhui,

48
